item.description: Get started # There are two main ways to get started with Doks: Tutorial # 👉 The Tutorial is intended for novice to intermediate users. Step-by-step instructions on how to start a new Doks project. Tutorial → Quick Start # 👉 The Quick Start is intended for intermediate to advanced users. One page summary of how to start a new Doks project. Quick Start → Go further # Recipes, Reference Guides, Extensions, and Showcase.
